snippet.title: Mega Drive Longplay [597] Super Mario World 64 (CN) (Unlicensed)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: KAGE-008

A hilarious Mario bootleg for the Genesis, complete with graphics lifted from the SNES game, but with random music added into it for some of the levels. Developer is unknown, though cartridges of this game exist.

Info: https://bootleggames.fandom.com/wiki/Super_Mario_World_64

Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
